Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:02.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HD8CEBB&\blur2\3c&H21130C&}聽到馬戲團的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:05.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H7F6D65&\bord0}大家都歡喜雀躍加快著腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:09.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HDEBFA8&\blur2\3c&H87634E&}我也跟著要跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:13.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HFDF7F1&\bord0}儘管自己並沒有門票
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:16.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HD2DBE0&\bord0}滿以為又要被訓斥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:20.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HD2DBE0&\bord0}默默地祈禱 僅僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:24.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H000000&\3c&HB6D7E1&\3a&H64&\blur1}我們總是碰撞傷痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:28.15,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HEAEBE1&\bord0}仍在奔跑在地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:31.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H3C5048&\3a&H64&\blur2}假如這樣假如那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:35.70,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HC2AFE0&}總是為自己尋找藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:43.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}編造一些能向別人說明的空話 又有什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an8}日子會是無限美好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:50.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H282524&\3c&H8D8B89&\3a&H64&\blur2\an8}這是我們懷著恐懼依然選擇的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:53.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H24292C&\3c&HB7CDD0&\3a&H64&\blur2\an8}我們向著你想去的地方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:58.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H232122&\bord0\an8}太陽就是為了今天而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:05.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\an8}每當心中萌生出寶石 就為它起一個最深刻的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:12.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\bord0\an8}即使不強大也是樂趣依舊 一如充滿淚水和歡笑的最初的日子
