Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒一醒 阿波羅！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐根！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙出現在了城鎮附近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 而且一起出現的還有大量魔物
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐根！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓我好擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成功了呢 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事真是太好了 歐根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也看到了 我好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是出大事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利維坦開始襲擊我們的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這邊已經要堅持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能趕上真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐根 也讓我們來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 雖然很感謝你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是人力能抵抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且牠身邊還有不少的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕緊帶城鎮裡的人去避難才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想救利維坦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想救牠？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利維坦已經到達了極限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:04:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠不斷地用自己的力量來淨化被污染的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在都用盡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了活下去就不得不去吃其他人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這其實不是它的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那些魔物才會來襲擊我們的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是由於牠召喚了魔物反而令牠更虛弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不抓緊時間的話 利維坦會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 歐根！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我們來幫忙救利維坦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有拯救牠的手段嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能去除現在折磨著利維坦的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠一定會找回自己的力量恢復原樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要搞定那條巨龍 牠身邊的魔物很礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望在場的各位盡可能去吸引魔物注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並削減牠們的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,華麗地大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 將你們的力量借給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 剛走出來就被攔住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 沒完沒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有點兒過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪麗 卡爾瓦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你們是在做什麼事 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 那麼我們來支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海神的加護消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水質變差的同時魚的數量也變少了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說想辦法解決那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能吃上魚了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓海洋變得乾乾淨淨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將這裡有名的魚全都吃上一頓再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你好強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不強啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 她很強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼神很真誠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有些事情必須要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那大姐姐我來幫助你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她化作蝴蝶飛走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但技術相當了得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在 我們走！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來是打算支援他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我們遇到了危機！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死胡同？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐姐們 你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,體壯如牛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛破 天衝！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰柱之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Icicle nail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 身後！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大炮沒了子彈還能近身肉搏 真方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐根！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 沒完沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊衝出這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在指望你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我好好幹活啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拳法真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子可是羅曼的求道者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等一下我們來用拳頭聊聊天吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些魔物有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 突然都聚在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉入防守了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快躲開！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 快撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭！討厭！討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 這是鬧哪樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然組織起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這看起來是有指揮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指揮？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是利維坦在指揮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺不到它在指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這感覺到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指揮者在那群魔物之中？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣根本沒辦法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要制止這玩意兒的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必須先將牠們的指揮官搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這種情況下根本沒法找…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞 你能召喚巴哈姆特一口氣滅了那東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈姆特的火焰會傷害到利維坦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼時候…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是琉米耶爾聖騎士團長 夏洛塔·菲妮婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:38.68,Default,NTP,0,450,0,,{\fs30}lumiel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來現在並不是悠哉聊天的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來我是打算靜觀其變的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看起來挺危險的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你們一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿維斯之槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.38,Default,NTP,0,170,0,,{\fs30}Arvess
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯現你的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙沒有散開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在找到牠們的指揮官將其消滅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐根！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 少年！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救利維坦吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 世界樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你怎麼了 露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會救你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厲害的嘛 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你一直在守護著這片海洋和生活在這座島上的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女兒被大浪沖走了下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你救了她並守護她了3天3夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜我的女兒已經離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以沒辦法告訴她你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因為有你 她才能活著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你了 利維坦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 利維坦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑騎士！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對露莉亞做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是從露莉亞那裡奪走了利維坦的一部分力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 那孩子和我一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那孩子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有關於我的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還不是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走了 人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘船是哪來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再失去她了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝天謝地 能順利解決真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎮子上的人們都能平安無事這比任何事都好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家能像這樣一起慶祝 是件幸福事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在了 在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪麗 卡爾瓦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們差不多該回旅店了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我們有緣再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼危險的陷阱我們一起踩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有緣再見嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會有機會的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,際遇啊緣分啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些可都是存在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 一定還會再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有想見的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和黑騎士一起的那個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能和那孩子說說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也許會更加了解自身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的我雖然很害怕知道自己的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在大家在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我們和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉卡姆 有在喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 看你這樣子沒少喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種日子必須喝個過癮才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是拯救了島嶼的英雄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別拿他開玩笑啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜你們所賜 海洋恢復了原貌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人會想到一個剛出道的騎空團能做到這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能預感到你們的團將會越發強大…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 你們幾個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 你這話是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒啥大不了的 我就直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是能帶上我一起旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶你一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然城鎮還要重建
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但剩下的工作只要當官的肯去各個島嶼奔波就能解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 你打算離開這座島嶼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說為什麼選擇加入我們團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這少年會吸引一些很有趣的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的事情是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要和某個人做一個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了你們的所作所為 我覺得這事不能再拖了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 我不會因為自己的私事而給你們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照 歐根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這決定做的真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐根如果能上船的話 我們也能更加安心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們受了你的不少照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正所謂出門靠夥伴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地也許並不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我覺得這也是某種緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們今後也會遇到更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想珍惜我們建立的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些都會在某處相連著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照 歐根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欠你一個人情了 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 嚴肅的談話到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始新團員的歡迎會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉卡姆 你還能繼續喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐 能喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也陪你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 卡塔莉娜也陪他們喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是個不錯的團嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你有考慮明天的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說嘛 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情好了酒才喝得香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才嫌棄大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 團長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來帶頭乾杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得有點小題大做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相當華麗的出航呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 這是你搞的鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是他們自己搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 再見！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還會回來吃好吃的魚的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 之後就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜你們所賜 這次順利解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城鎮裡的人也精神得很
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家能找回笑容 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們前往下一個島嶼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這片廣闊天空的盡頭 到底有什麼在等著我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們親眼去看一看吧！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 另一個天空
